_:N4a4c73b1fec4424ab5c38581a2163d4f <http://schema.org/description> "The Health Research Authority (HRA) protects and promotes the interests of patients and the public in health research. HRA is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department of Health and Social Care ." .
